headline: Oppenheimer upgrades Mosaic on cost cuts and portfolio optimization
summary: Investing.com -- Oppenheimer upgraded The Mosaic Company (NYSE:MOS) to Outperform from Perform and set a price target of $33 given the fertilizer maker’s efforts to reduce costs, optimize its product portfolio, and boost production efficiency as key drivers of future growth.

headline: Here's Why You Should Retain Mosaic Stock in Your Portfolio
